{
  "name": "context-recall",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "智能记忆系统，自动捕获会话摘要、基于查询检索相关上下文、管理分层记忆存储（日/周/月）。零外部依赖，本地优先设计。",
  "description_en": "Smart memory system for OpenClaw agents with auto-capture, semantic retrieval, and tiered storage. Zero external dependencies, local-first design.",
  "author": "OpenClaw Community",
  "license": "MIT",
  "keywords": ["memory", "context", "recall", "session", "persistence", "中文"],
